title: Motley Fool Money: 11.20.2009
description: Tim Geithner takes some heat.  Dell delivers some disappointment.   And the Mortgage Bankers Association delivers more bad news on the mortgage front.  In this installment of Motley Fool Money, we tackle those stories, share three stocks on our radar, and discuss whether there will be a “new normal”.
